{"tid":1869973,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"第二波工業行動即將強勢登場！召集各運輸界手足加入公會！罷工基金已經成立！","createTime":"2020-02-08T13:20:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-10T04:22:26.000Z","uid":345458,"like":71,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":66,"replies":[{"pid":"bf27758b9bce67caac1a3c2b23ba36a7cdabec8d","tid":1869973,"uid":345458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T13:20:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><ins>1. 巴士篇：</ins></span></span><br />\n「巴士業職工會聯盟」於本月3號已經表示<span style=\"color: red;\">若醫護罷工未能促使政府進行全面封關，</span>將開展籌備緊急大會表決罷工！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2DViZeD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2DViZeD.png&h=f2658ece&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n聯盟由<ins><span style=\"color: violet;\">新世界第一巴士職工會</span></ins>，<ins><span style=\"color: violet;\">城巴有限公司職工會</span></ins>，<ins><span style=\"color: violet;\">九巴員工協會</span></ins>組成。會員包括九巴，新巴，城巴的全職/兼職員工，有機會影響超過<span style=\"color: red;\">九成</span>巴士路線！<br />\n目前<ins><span style=\"color: violet;\">龍運</span></ins>同<ins><span style=\"color: violet;\">嶼巴</span></ins>仲未有相關工會，而呢兩間公司既巴士路線亦係高危！<span style=\"color: red;\">請相關人士開始籌備工會</span>，以保障自己！<br />\n<br />\n<ins>以下係高危巴士「運毒」路線：</ins><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">所有機場路線</span>(城巴、龍運)<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">所有深圳灣路線</span>(嶼巴 B2、B2P、B2X / 城巴 B3、B3A、B3M、B3X)<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">所有港珠澳路線</span>(嶼巴 B4、B6/城巴 B5及途經的機場巴士）<br />\n以上路線行走餘下<span style=\"color: red;\">仍未封關路線</span>(機場、深圳灣、港珠澳)，深入社區「運毒」到家門！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><ins>2. 黨鐵篇：</ins></span></span><br />\n「港鐵新動力」尋日(7/2)已經召開咗特別會員大會，並<span style=\"color: red;\">已經通過</span>咗工業行動議案，將會推出詳細內容！<br />\n<br />\n黨鐵截至2018有17700位員工(不計海外員工)，但而家會員人數不足1000！(好似係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">好黃</span><span style=\"color: gold;\">既前線肯出嚟未啊？</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GnanGsu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGnanGsu.jpg&h=6572de63&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><ins>3. 航空篇：</ins></span></span> <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">(8/2 20:49更新)</span><br />\n「港龍航空公司空勤人員協會」今日(8/2)已經召開咗緊急會員大會，關於是否支持並授權工會進行工業行動，結果為<span style=\"color: red;\">贊成通過</span>。但工會決定<span style=\"color: red;\">暫時不進行罷工</span>，並表示會有其他相關工業行動。<br />\n<br />\n工會同時強調，由於已得到會員授權工會進行工業行動，因此不排除當<span style=\"color: red;\">有更足夠會員人數支持後</span>，會發動即時罷工。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1Yg2GMR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1Yg2GMR.png&h=f8915ff5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">多班國泰和港龍航空客機</span>，因有機上乘客曾赴湖北武漢或懷疑感染肺炎，影響全機其他乘客和機組人員滯留內地。至少有6名機組人員返港後，被視為密切接觸者，被衞生署勒令送往隔離營。<br />\n工會曾多次對於國泰只停飛九成航班表示不滿，<span style=\"color: red;\">要求全面停飛</span>，以確保員工安全。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><ins>相關連結：</ins></span></span><br />\n🙌「巴士業職工會聯盟」 FB專頁：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/busunionsfederation.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fbusunionsfederation.hk%2F&d=KH9yB5wEnJvJbT5Qn4WrOmLZ6li1RkmcNQmTobTGNbY%3D&h=6ec04918\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/busunionsfederation.hk/</a><br />\n🚌「新世界第一巴士職工會」FB專頁：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/NewWorldFirstBusCompanyStaffUnion/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FNewWorldFirstBusCompanyStaffUnion%2F&d=KH9yB5wEnJvJbT5Qn4WrOmLZ6li1RkmcNQmTobTGNbY%3D&h=bfee0cd4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/NewWorldFirstBusCompanyStaffUnion/</a><br />\n🚌「城巴有限公司職工會」FB專頁：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/CitybusLimitedEmployeesUnion/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FCitybusLimitedEmployeesUnion%2F&d=KH9yB5wEnJvJbT5Qn4WrOmLZ6li1RkmcNQmTobTGNbY%3D&h=fad02aca\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/CitybusLimitedEmployeesUnion/</a><br />\n🚌「九巴員工協會」FB專頁：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/%E4%B9%9D%E5%B7%B4%E5%93%A1%E5%B7%A5%E5%8D%94%E6%9C%83%E6%9C%83%E5%93%A1%E5%B0%88%E9%A0%81-156670821160022/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F%25E4%25B9%259D%25E5%25B7%25B4%25E5%2593%25A1%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E5%258D%2594%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%259C%2583%25E5%2593%25A1%25E5%25B0%2588%25E9%25A0%2581-156670821160022%2F&d=KH9yB5wEnJvJbT5Qn4WrOmLZ6li1RkmcNQmTobTGNbY%3D&h=d30a6c4a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/%E4%B9%9D%E5%B7%B4%E5%93%A1%E5%B7%A5%E5%8D%94%E6%9C%83%E6%9C%83%E5%93%A1%E5%B0%88%E9%A0%81-156670821160022/</a><br />\n📋問卷：城巴及新巴員工對武漢肺炎防疫措施之意見及工業行動意向 <br />\n<a href=\"https://forms.gle/cC7vf1T3vQPmNntv6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FcC7vf1T3vQPmNntv6&d=KH9yB5wEnJvJbT5Qn4WrOmLZ6li1RkmcNQmTobTGNbY%3D&h=43e1c073\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/cC7vf1T3vQPmNntv6</a><br />\n<br />\n🚟「港鐵新動力」FB專頁：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/railwaypowerrp/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Frailwaypowerrp%2F&d=KH9yB5wEnJvJbT5Qn4WrOmLZ6li1RkmcNQmTobTGNbY%3D&h=825f2477\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/railwaypowerrp/</a><br />\n<br />\n✈️「港龍航空公司空勤人員協會」FB專頁：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/kafaahk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fkafaahk%2F&d=KH9yB5wEnJvJbT5Qn4WrOmLZ6li1RkmcNQmTobTGNbY%3D&h=ed0a396d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/kafaahk/</a><br />\n<br />\n以下只係小弟粗略整合 有任何錯誤請指正！<br />\n如果搵唔到入會form可以講低！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">第二波工業行動即將登場！</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img s